# Quick Start — Run These Commands

## 1. Installér Ollama
```bash
# Download fra https://ollama.com/download og installér
ollama pull mistral
```

## 2. Opsæt projektet
```bash
git clone <dit-repo-url>
cd course-study-assistant
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate        # Windows: venv\Scripts\activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

## 3. Læg dokumenter i mappen
```bash
cp dine-noter.pdf documents/
```

## 4. Start
```bash
# Terminal 1
ollama serve

# Terminal 2
source venv/bin/activate
uvicorn app.main:app --reload --port 8000
```

## 5. Åbn
```
http://localhost:8000
```

Upload filer → Stil spørgsmål → Få svar.
